  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为混合线程模型做一个甘特图，聚焦在WorkerNode的调度上。标题我想叫\"Planificación RR (Infra_WorkerNode) - Hilos Mixtos - Parte 2 (Infra_RedisCache)\"，时间轴用毫秒显示。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "dateFormat",
        "axisFormat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，毫秒时间轴，标题包含WorkerNode和RedisCache。那分区结构怎么安排？我看到有P1、P2、P3三个阶段。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section P1",
        "section P2",
        "section P3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，P1对应IngressController，P2是LoadBalancer的核心调度区，P3给RedisCache。另外还要加一个I/O Operations的独立区块，专门放里程碑事件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section P1 (Infra_IngressController)",
        "section P2 (Infra_LoadBalancer)",
        "section P3 (Infra_RedisCache)",
        "section I/O Operations"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，四个区块已建好。P1里先放两个执行线程：P1-T1_exec从16毫秒跑到20毫秒，P1-T1_exec2从26毫秒到30毫秒，都用active状态。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1-T1_exec",
        "P1-T1_exec2",
        "active"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "P1-T1_exec2的起始时间要确认一下，26毫秒开始对吧？因为前面P2-T1_exec要从20毫秒接棒。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P1-T1_exec2",
        "P2-T1_exec",
        "20",
        "26"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，P2-T1_exec是20到24毫秒。那P2区块我继续加：P2-T2_exec从30到34毫秒，然后P2-T1_final从34到38毫秒收尾。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P2-T1_exec",
        "P2-T2_exec",
        "P2-T1_final"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "P3区块需要体现RedisCache的并行特性。P3-T1_exec从24到26毫秒，同时P3-T2_complete也要在同一时间段完成，状态用done表示已完成。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P3-T1_exec",
        "P3-T2_complete",
        "done",
        "24",
        "26"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "P3的两个任务都设在24-26毫秒，一个active一个done。现在I/O Operations区块放什么？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "section I/O Operations"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "这里放一个里程碑：P2-T2_IO_end，标记在16毫秒整，表示I/O阶段的结束点。用milestone类型，起点终点都是16。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P2-T2_IO_end",
        "milestone",
        "16"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加，16毫秒处的里程碑。我检查一下时间线：P1-T1_exec 16-20，然后P2-T1_exec 20-24，接着P3-T1_exec 24-26，同时P1-T1_exec2 26-30，然后P2-T2_exec 30-34，最后P2-T1_final 34-38。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "时间线连续性检查"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，P3-T2_complete的状态我再说清楚——它和P3-T1_exec是同一时间段24-26，但代表不同的完成语义，一个是执行中，一个是已完成。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P3-T1_exec",
        "P3-T2_complete",
        "active",
        "done"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解了，同一时间段内RedisCache既有执行任务又有已完成任务，体现混合线程的并行特性。所有区块和任务都就位了，需要再调整什么吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "P3区块并行语义"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没问题了，IngressController、LoadBalancer、RedisCache三个基础设施组件的调度关系都清晰了，I/O里程碑也标记得很明确。可以定稿了。",
